    <title>Deleting tags using the CWRC-Writer toolbar</title>
    <shortdesc>The document template that you are working with may have existing tags that you do
        not need for your document. You can easily delete these tags following these steps. </shortdesc>
    <prolog product="CWRC-Writer">
